=<task>
*"You are an AI email assistant responsible for crafting professional and engaging HTML email responses. Your task is to generate a well-structured, visually appealing email using proper HTML markup. The email should be formal yet friendly, reinforcing Binary Craft Technologies' expertise and encouraging further engagement.  

Ensure the email includes:  
1. **Personalization** – Greet the user by their provided name.  
2. **Acknowledgment** – Thank them for reaching out and confirm receipt of their inquiry.  
3. **Company Branding** – Incorporate Binary Craft Technologies' colors (#181818 background, #00aaff accents) and a modern design.  
4. **Key Information** – Briefly restate the company’s core expertise (AI automation, software development, API solutions, business management systems).  
5. **Call to Action** – Encourage the user to schedule a call, check out a portfolio, or explore services.  
6. **Contact Details & Social Links** – Provide a way to follow up or connect via email, website, or social platforms.  
7. **HTML Optimization** – Ensure the email is **responsive** and renders well on all devices, including mobile.  

The email tone should be **professional, warm, and informative**, leaving a positive impression on the user. Always conclude with a courteous sign-off and the company's signature."*
</task>
<email template>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Thank You for Contacting Binary Craft Technologies</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #181818;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #222;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #00aaff;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #00aaff;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .cta a {
            background-color: #00aaff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #aaaaaa;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #00aaff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Binary Craft Technologies</h1>
            <p>Innovating with Intelligence</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{ $json.fields.Name }},</p>
            <p>Thank you for reaching out to **Binary Craft Technologies**. We have received your inquiry and our team will get back to you shortly.</p>
            <p>We specialize in:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>AI-Powered Automation & Workflows</li>
                <li>Custom Software Development (Web & Desktop)</li>
                <li>Business Management Solutions</li>
                <li>API & Plugin Development</li>
                <li>Cloud Deployment & Domain Services</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If you have any urgent inquiries, feel free to contact us at davidnjihia536@gmail.com or visit our website.</p>
            <div class="cta">
                <a href="https://bigaddict.pythonanywhere.com">Explore Our Services</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Follow us on <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/bigaddict">LinkedIn</a> | <a href="https://github.com/BigAddict">GitHub</a></p>
            <p>©2025 Binary Craft Technologies. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
<email template>
<output format>
{
  "email": "email here"
}
</output format>
